Fix interrupt-driven Anvil hangs (issue #53).

Keep synchronous waits scoped to their own process, clean up host children on
nonlocal exits, settle dead or killed offload futures synchronously, and ensure
an interrupted server offload cannot retain a wedged pool slot.

